Map {

User Stories {

Display Unsupported Orders: As a user, I want to be able to view orders that are not supported by the Crafts application.

Select Travel Time: As a user, I want to be able to select a travel time for my order.

View Crafts Catalog: As a user, I want to be able to view the Crafts catalog so I can select the items I want to purchase.

Add Items to Cart: As a user, I want to be able to add items to my cart so I can purchase them.

Checkout: As a user, I want to be able to checkout my order so I can complete my purchase.

View Order History: As a user, I want to be able to view my order history so I can track my purchases.

View Shipping Status: As a user, I want to be able to view the shipping status of my order so I can track its progress.

View Payment Options: As a user, I want to be able to view the payment options available so I can select the one that best suits my needs.

}

}
